AI Assist

We believe in a tech-driven, AI-powered productivity expert with perfect memory whose sole mission is to make your work easier and to make sure you don't miss a beat. Here, we have summarized the main points.

Spiky/Differentiated Points of View

* AI can catch us up on what we missed while we were offline.
* We want to have searchable, full-text, on-demand access to information.
* We want to easily handle interruptions, low process times, high load, and fast context and task switching.
* We understand that there isn't a lot to learn that isn't about providing organized data. What is left is more about filtering out the chaff to get to what you really need: curated, reliable information and a deeper understanding.
* The power of information is knowing how to productively work without friction and adapt best practices.
* We consider our interaction with the AI in ChatGPT to be a series of informed and precise queries, capable of managing complex tasks without the need for direct human intervention.

Who are the users, and what outcome do they desire?

* We want to see the future of AI to be not just about providing scripted content. We believe in unique and different thinking that can change the world with our unique and original ideas. What makes us special is our dedication to tools, creativity, and productivity for every idea. Tools, technology, and transformations are productivity tools with workflows and about best practices of implementing AI in tools.
* The power of technology is amazing with the AI Cloud that is effortless and simple just as our tools are made for you.
